articles.title: Williamson century guides New Zealand to crucial World Test Championship victory - ICC Cricket
articles.description: The Kiwi veteran batted the entire fourth day to score yet another Test century that ensured his side cruised home against South Africa.
articles.content:
It sets up a crucial top-of-the-standings battle between the Kiwis and Australia later this month, with the two trans-Tasman rivals set to battle it out in a two-Test series in New Zealand.
